author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! A month ago as a Canadian I looked a spat between my greatest neighbor to the south. I had great hopes that these tense relations would cool down, but after weeks of hearing about becoming the 51st state, it's time to talk a little bit about why this is all so wrong. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: Things Have Gotten So Much Worse...
